{"tid":2017370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日提醒左我地一定要撐民間記者會","createTime":"2020-05-15T05:14:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T09:14:43.000Z","uid":50674,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4a161694e952d13adccf9247ee58f6df8403ff33","tid":2017370,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"頭先有手足開post話 大口狗揀呢個時間指陳健波做內會 係要蓋過民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n咁講一言驚醒夢中人 本身都無發覺民間記者會咁重要 港共咁大件事都係為左打擊民間記者會 證明一定要力撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前電視台會直播 而家冇左 但唔代表唔重要ga 我地更加要靠自己撐ar<br />\n<br />\n熱狗鬧佢地搞大台 咁民間記者會就係要統一民間聲音對抗極權政府 仲要教導市民大眾 如果有幾十個記者會咁仲邊有力量ar<br />\n<br />\n之前好多人唔知35+同功能組別 政府完全唔驚lor 民間記者會就開記者會代表香港人同政府講 我地會團結一致進攻功能組別 搶到35+重奪立法會 大大聲同政府講我地唔會認輸ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好再聽熱狗話咩民間記者會係泛民議員助理 唔講都冇比機會人地澄清<br />\n就算係又點 泛民助理都可以係手足 鄺仔都出黎la<br />\n況且我地係要建制輸 唔係泛民贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e66a278573aa4f0465ef5fd55d0d1ee64a7a1a","tid":2017370,"uid":50674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:17:17.000Z","msg":"巴打嗰個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2017271\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2017271</a>"},{"pid":"272d40b7b15009b0cf4f89097cffcc9beb2f5a63","tid":2017370,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c1ecbd4f89c40cf7de4c230cbb6f709f5c3a081","tid":2017370,"uid":49329,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"一定要有講真相嘅民間記者會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/